data.title: Potential malware? AVG logs shows that it is constantly blocking 'System' and 'SVCHOST.exe'
data.meta_description: Hi. I was noticing a couple of days ago that my chrome every now and again was failing to connect to the internet despite the internet being fine (Xbox live was still running, phone WiFi worked and could connect to internet). So i knew something was up. I've tried several malware detector softwar...
